WEBVTT

00:00:11.105 --> 00:00:13.465
The view is beautiful.
It would be even better with a lover.

00:00:13.545 --> 00:00:16.225
And… do you have one?

00:00:16.305 --> 00:00:18.585
Just broke up with her. I proposed to her.

00:00:18.665 --> 00:00:20.985
And she said she would work in Vietnam.

00:00:21.065 --> 00:00:22.105
So, she turned me down.

00:00:22.185 --> 00:00:24.985
-When will you stop picking on me?
-Your banana cake is trash!

00:00:25.065 --> 00:00:26.105
That’s it!

00:00:26.185 --> 00:00:28.545
Did you see him?!
He was trying to screw with me!

00:00:28.625 --> 00:00:29.465
Nava, stop!

00:00:29.545 --> 00:00:31.345
Ever thought? If you weren't like this,

00:00:31.425 --> 00:00:32.584
you might've already been his boyfriend.

00:00:32.665 --> 00:00:35.105
But I don't know how he feels about me.

00:00:35.185 --> 00:00:37.465
What made you decide
to seek treatment with me?

00:00:37.545 --> 00:00:39.265
I want to get cured from this condition.

00:00:39.345 --> 00:00:41.025
He doesn't seem ready at all.

00:03:03.345 --> 00:03:04.945
HOW ARE YOU DOING?

00:03:05.025 --> 00:03:07.665
YOU CAN TELL ME ANYTHING.

00:03:32.705 --> 00:03:37.185
HOW ARE YOU DOING?
YOU CAN TELL ME ANYTHING.

00:04:08.745 --> 00:04:15.625
I’M SORRY, PI DOC,
BUT I DON'T WANT TO DO THIS ANYMORE.

00:04:25.945 --> 00:04:26.945
Bravo!

00:04:28.625 --> 00:04:30.705
Thank you. See you next time.

00:04:34.385 --> 00:04:35.905
COME TO MY SHOP, OR I’LL CUT YOUR PAY.

00:04:35.985 --> 00:04:39.025
What the hell is wrong with him?

00:05:20.745 --> 00:05:21.865
You’re wasted.

00:05:25.905 --> 00:05:27.145
What do you want?

00:05:27.985 --> 00:05:29.025
Nothing.

00:05:30.025 --> 00:05:31.505
Can't I just want you to be here?

00:05:33.065 --> 00:05:36.225
Just spit it out. I’ve got work to do.

00:05:45.625 --> 00:05:47.025
Drink with me first.

00:05:47.545 --> 00:05:48.905
Or else…

00:05:49.465 --> 00:05:50.505
I’m cutting your pay.

00:05:53.265 --> 00:05:54.625
What the hell is your problem?

00:05:56.465 --> 00:05:58.145
I just want someone to drink with.

00:06:00.385 --> 00:06:01.665
Go ahead and cut my pay.

00:06:02.385 --> 00:06:03.665
I'm not drinking.

00:06:06.625 --> 00:06:07.465
You…

00:06:10.585 --> 00:06:12.625
You want a piece of me? Hmm?

00:06:13.865 --> 00:06:15.105
Do whatever you want.

00:07:10.905 --> 00:07:12.825
I just wanted someone to drink with.

00:07:15.425 --> 00:07:17.465
Can’t you stay and drink with me?

00:07:58.065 --> 00:08:00.225
Oh, Auntie Phailin. Tawan, wake up.

00:08:00.305 --> 00:08:02.825
It’s okay. No need to wake him.

00:08:02.905 --> 00:08:04.065
Let him sleep.

00:08:11.785 --> 00:08:15.625
I just came to check if he was here.

00:08:16.225 --> 00:08:19.505
He didn't pick up my calls,
and he didn't call back either.

00:08:21.305 --> 00:08:25.265
He probably had his phone on silent.

00:08:26.505 --> 00:08:29.265
But he's been here with me.
Not going anywhere.

00:08:30.105 --> 00:08:31.185
I see.

00:08:31.905 --> 00:08:33.505
You two are quite something.

00:08:34.305 --> 00:08:36.545
The other day
you almost wrecked the kitchen.

00:08:37.425 --> 00:08:38.705
When did you two become so close?

00:08:43.465 --> 00:08:45.665
But it's good. Stay on good terms.

00:08:48.305 --> 00:08:51.385
Now, get me a drink, dear. On the rocks.

00:08:53.265 --> 00:08:54.665
Coming right up, Ma’am.

00:09:10.305 --> 00:09:11.185
Here you go.

00:09:11.265 --> 00:09:12.385
Thank you.

00:09:22.345 --> 00:09:27.945
Tawan might act tough on the outside,
not as gentle as his siblings.

00:09:29.185 --> 00:09:33.105
But he’s actually a very kind person.

00:09:35.305 --> 00:09:39.865
If he ever does anything
to hurt your feelings,

00:09:39.945 --> 00:09:41.225
please don't take it to heart.

00:09:42.705 --> 00:09:44.985
Sometimes, he just doesn't know

00:09:45.065 --> 00:09:47.185
how to show kindness to others.

00:09:51.105 --> 00:09:52.065
I won't.

00:09:53.225 --> 00:09:54.585
I don't mind it at all.

00:09:55.905 --> 00:09:56.985
Thank you.

00:09:58.065 --> 00:10:01.145
Please take care of Tawan.

00:10:06.505 --> 00:10:07.705
Yes.

00:10:08.505 --> 00:10:09.785
I'll take care of him, Auntie.

00:10:13.025 --> 00:10:14.145
Thank you.

00:10:19.625 --> 00:10:20.465
Shall we?

00:10:33.385 --> 00:10:34.585
Come, lie down properly.

00:11:47.025 --> 00:11:47.985
I went to therapy…

00:11:49.505 --> 00:11:50.345
And…?

00:11:53.985 --> 00:11:55.025
…but it's not working.

00:11:57.305 --> 00:11:59.585
Treatment doesn't work in just one go.

00:11:59.665 --> 00:12:01.385
It takes time.

00:12:02.265 --> 00:12:04.105
We're all rooting for you, man.

00:12:04.185 --> 00:12:06.225
Come on, you can do this.

00:12:11.665 --> 00:12:14.385
Look, there's your Pi Doc.

00:12:17.265 --> 00:12:19.985
Pi Doc! Over here!

00:12:21.265 --> 00:12:22.425
James, hold this for me.

00:12:22.505 --> 00:12:23.585
What?

00:12:28.065 --> 00:12:29.265
Sailom!

00:12:29.345 --> 00:12:30.745
Where are you going?

00:12:38.625 --> 00:12:40.025
Please look after this for me.

00:12:44.145 --> 00:12:45.665
-Thank you.
-Alright.

00:12:50.385 --> 00:12:51.705
Are you thinking what I’m thinking?

00:12:52.225 --> 00:12:54.345
Something’s up with those two.

00:12:54.425 --> 00:12:56.945
It’s so obvious.
You could see it from Pluto.

00:12:59.985 --> 00:13:01.385
Now we have four bikes.

00:13:01.465 --> 00:13:02.785
How can we practice cycling?

00:13:04.105 --> 00:13:05.345
We wait.

00:13:14.305 --> 00:13:15.545
Sailom, what’s wrong?

00:13:19.905 --> 00:13:21.225
Nothing!

00:13:22.905 --> 00:13:25.545
Even if something was wrong,
why would you even care?!

00:13:27.665 --> 00:13:30.985
Sailom, calm down and listen to me.

00:13:34.065 --> 00:13:36.905
Can you tell me what happened?

00:13:38.425 --> 00:13:40.825
Why did you decide to stop the treatment?

00:13:45.985 --> 00:13:47.385
Whether I continue…

00:13:48.665 --> 00:13:49.985
or not,

00:13:50.705 --> 00:13:53.465
it’s my business. Stay out of it.

00:13:56.145 --> 00:13:58.185
But you told me before…

00:13:59.465 --> 00:14:00.865
that you wanted to get better.

00:14:04.825 --> 00:14:07.425
Are you afraid the treatment won't work?

00:14:08.305 --> 00:14:12.185
If that's the case, please trust me.

00:14:13.145 --> 00:14:15.305
Once we start,

00:14:16.185 --> 00:14:18.785
you will definitely recover.

00:14:19.545 --> 00:14:21.225
Look at it like riding a bike.

00:14:22.505 --> 00:14:24.665
If you have a clear destination,

00:14:25.305 --> 00:14:27.625
you might face some
obstacles along the way.

00:14:28.145 --> 00:14:30.025
But if you don't stop

00:14:30.105 --> 00:14:32.025
riding and keep going,

00:14:33.225 --> 00:14:35.665
you’ll reach the finish line one day.

00:14:40.785 --> 00:14:44.385
You have to be brave enough
to leave the past behind.

00:14:47.505 --> 00:14:48.505
Pi Doc…

00:14:50.705 --> 00:14:52.825
I agreed to the treatment because

00:14:55.265 --> 00:14:57.945
I thought you could make me better.

00:15:02.065 --> 00:15:04.105
But you refused to treat me yourself.

00:15:06.945 --> 00:15:11.185
If this treatment is like
riding a bike, as you just said.

00:15:14.105 --> 00:15:15.105
Now,

00:15:17.505 --> 00:15:20.145
you’ve cycled far away and left me behind.

00:15:51.545 --> 00:15:52.385
Doc.

00:15:54.065 --> 00:15:56.545
Pi Doc. Hey.

00:15:56.625 --> 00:15:58.345
Hey, Doctor!

00:15:59.145 --> 00:16:01.025
-Yeah?
-Why are you spacing out?

00:16:04.425 --> 00:16:05.985
Yeah, what’s up with you?

00:16:14.305 --> 00:16:16.145
I don't even know where to start.

00:16:18.225 --> 00:16:19.865
You're acting weird.

00:16:23.345 --> 00:16:25.585
Sailom wants me to be his doctor.

00:16:28.905 --> 00:16:30.545
Then what's the problem?

00:16:30.625 --> 00:16:31.905
Just treat him.

00:16:33.785 --> 00:16:35.865
If only it were that simple.

00:16:38.105 --> 00:16:39.705
It's just…

00:16:43.585 --> 00:16:45.825
He thought of me as
more than just doctor and patient.

00:16:50.185 --> 00:16:51.185
What did you do?

00:16:53.345 --> 00:16:55.945
I transferred his case to another doctor.

00:16:56.745 --> 00:16:58.265
I can't do it.

00:16:59.105 --> 00:17:00.505
It’s medical ethics.

00:17:02.505 --> 00:17:03.705
But now he’s furious

00:17:05.505 --> 00:17:06.704
and refusing all treatment.

00:17:10.345 --> 00:17:11.985
I'm at my wits' end.

00:17:13.625 --> 00:17:14.464
Listen, Doc.

00:17:15.785 --> 00:17:17.424
If he refuses treatment,

00:17:17.505 --> 00:17:19.105
that's on him. It's his life.

00:17:21.464 --> 00:17:22.745
But I want him to get better.

00:17:24.105 --> 00:17:27.345
Because if he doesn't recover,
I don't see how he'll survive out there.

00:17:28.945 --> 00:17:30.345
I don't want to see him suffer anymore.

00:17:51.065 --> 00:17:52.305
Guys, listen.

00:17:53.665 --> 00:17:58.825
When I said I wanted to quit
being a host, I meant it. I'm done.

00:17:59.545 --> 00:18:02.585
Why? You’ve earned a lot from that.

00:18:05.865 --> 00:18:06.945
Yeah.

00:18:07.505 --> 00:18:08.745
Nah,

00:18:09.425 --> 00:18:11.185
I feel like I found something

00:18:11.265 --> 00:18:14.505
more important than money.

00:18:16.745 --> 00:18:17.585
You dating someone?

00:18:20.665 --> 00:18:22.345
I can’t really call it that yet.

00:18:25.705 --> 00:18:27.865
I just want to prove to him

00:18:27.945 --> 00:18:29.865
that he's the only one for me.

00:18:31.905 --> 00:18:33.265
Damn…

00:18:33.985 --> 00:18:35.625
I wanna see the face of the guy

00:18:35.705 --> 00:18:38.425
who tamed the legendary Sky.

00:18:39.825 --> 00:18:41.105
I met him at the club.

00:18:41.185 --> 00:18:44.545
He’s a client, nothing like the others.

00:18:45.945 --> 00:18:47.065
Get it? It’s like…

00:18:48.705 --> 00:18:50.585
-A client?
-Yeah.

00:18:52.305 --> 00:18:54.065
Are you sure you want to date a client?

00:18:58.025 --> 00:19:00.465
I don't know if it's a good idea or not.

00:19:05.145 --> 00:19:06.665
All I know is…

00:19:08.305 --> 00:19:09.265
I like him.

00:19:20.785 --> 00:19:21.785
Thanks, man.

00:19:23.585 --> 00:19:24.625
Wait a sec…

00:19:25.345 --> 00:19:27.425
One loves his patient.

00:19:27.505 --> 00:19:29.065
The other falls for a client.

00:19:29.745 --> 00:19:30.985
And you say thanks?

00:19:32.025 --> 00:19:32.905
What the heck?

00:19:34.745 --> 00:19:36.745
It’s simple, Tawan.

00:19:36.825 --> 00:19:38.745
If you love someone,

00:19:38.825 --> 00:19:42.345
you must let them know.

00:19:42.425 --> 00:19:44.625
Don't leave them guessing

00:19:44.705 --> 00:19:48.265
how they feel about you
or you feel about them.

00:19:48.345 --> 00:19:52.585
Otherwise, that love might turn into hate.

00:19:55.625 --> 00:19:58.065
Hey! Are you lagging?

00:19:58.145 --> 00:19:59.025
Why?

00:19:59.545 --> 00:20:00.985
Got someone on your mind?

00:20:04.385 --> 00:20:06.425
Tell us.

00:20:07.545 --> 00:20:08.625
I do.

00:20:10.185 --> 00:20:11.665
But I'm not into "talking."

00:20:12.225 --> 00:20:14.745
-I'm into "doing it."
-Whoa, damn!

00:20:14.825 --> 00:20:15.865
Which is your fav position?

00:20:15.945 --> 00:20:18.225
That’s wicked.

00:20:24.385 --> 00:20:27.225
Ouch!

00:20:28.825 --> 00:20:30.665
-Hey!
-It’s them, Tawan!

00:20:31.305 --> 00:20:32.945
-Get’em!
-Go on!

00:20:40.305 --> 00:20:41.345
Ouch!

00:20:42.025 --> 00:20:43.225
Hold still, will you?

00:20:43.305 --> 00:20:44.745
Then be more gentle, will you?

00:20:48.985 --> 00:20:51.745
Man… you shouldn't have messed
with his girlfriend.

00:20:51.825 --> 00:20:53.065
You almost got killed.

00:20:53.705 --> 00:20:56.305
How was I supposed to know?

00:20:56.385 --> 00:20:58.065
She said they were already over!

00:20:58.945 --> 00:21:01.305
Gosh, you shouldn't have done that.

00:21:01.825 --> 00:21:02.665
So what?

00:21:03.625 --> 00:21:05.425
Stop moving. Let me fix your wound.

00:21:09.945 --> 00:21:11.545
That stings!

00:21:11.625 --> 00:21:13.705
Dammit! I wouldn't have helped you!

00:21:13.785 --> 00:21:16.225
And who asked for your help?
I didn't ask for it!

00:21:17.185 --> 00:21:19.865
Look at yourself! And you’re still cocky!

00:21:19.945 --> 00:21:21.025
So what?!

00:21:21.105 --> 00:21:22.545
Both of you, stop arguing!

00:21:23.265 --> 00:21:24.105
Fine, fine!

00:21:24.185 --> 00:21:26.265
But don't you dare tell Mom!

00:21:26.345 --> 00:21:28.065
I don't want another lecture!

00:21:28.665 --> 00:21:30.545
Deal. If we tell,

00:21:31.065 --> 00:21:32.025
we're all dead anyway.

00:21:32.985 --> 00:21:36.065
Whoever breaks it does
the dishes for a whole month!

00:21:36.745 --> 00:21:38.385
-Promise.
-Promise.

00:21:38.465 --> 00:21:39.305
‎Promise!

00:21:50.865 --> 00:21:51.865
Cheers!

00:21:53.105 --> 00:21:54.225
Bluetooth!

00:22:05.945 --> 00:22:09.545
TANWARIN HOSPITAL

00:22:50.025 --> 00:22:51.705
I'm thinking about quitting my host job.

00:22:57.385 --> 00:22:58.345
Why?

00:22:59.705 --> 00:23:01.625
I just… don't want to do it anymore.

00:23:08.705 --> 00:23:11.585
How are your wounds? Still hurting?

00:23:12.745 --> 00:23:13.825
A little.

00:23:18.025 --> 00:23:19.225
Have you eaten yet?

00:23:21.345 --> 00:23:22.385
Not yet.

00:23:23.265 --> 00:23:24.465
Well…

00:23:24.545 --> 00:23:25.825
Want to grab some food?

00:23:27.865 --> 00:23:28.705
Aren’t you still mad at me?

00:23:29.905 --> 00:23:32.025
I am, but I’m hungry.

00:23:43.185 --> 00:23:44.385
Thank you. Here, the rice vermicelli.

00:23:45.105 --> 00:23:47.385
-What did you order for yourself?
-Instant noodles.

00:23:47.465 --> 00:23:49.265
OPEN

00:23:57.745 --> 00:23:59.185
No seasoning needed, I think.

00:23:59.265 --> 00:24:01.585
None. This place is legit.

00:24:02.145 --> 00:24:03.185
I must try.

00:24:04.545 --> 00:24:05.865
This is great.

00:24:12.145 --> 00:24:13.065
It's strange…

00:24:14.825 --> 00:24:18.905
I… I never thought of eating a meal
with you without alcohol.

00:24:20.905 --> 00:24:21.745
It’s nice.

00:24:22.665 --> 00:24:23.785
What nice?

00:24:26.585 --> 00:24:27.825
Just…

00:24:29.025 --> 00:24:30.705
eating in peace,

00:24:33.465 --> 00:24:35.065
no loud music,

00:24:36.305 --> 00:24:37.665
no one bothering us,

00:24:39.025 --> 00:24:42.985
and I don't have to
keep entertaining everyone.

00:24:44.505 --> 00:24:46.705
I usually eat alone.

00:24:47.345 --> 00:24:51.105
But… having you here as a friend
isn't bad either.

00:24:52.585 --> 00:24:54.505
Wait… friend?

00:24:54.585 --> 00:24:56.065
So we're friends now?

00:24:56.145 --> 00:24:57.905
Yeah, of course.

00:25:02.745 --> 00:25:04.025
Say "Ah."

00:25:04.825 --> 00:25:05.705
Eat this.

00:25:06.465 --> 00:25:07.625
Feeding you as a friend.

00:25:08.465 --> 00:25:09.825
Friend?

00:25:14.945 --> 00:25:17.145
If you weren’t my friend,
I wouldn’t share my meatballs with you.

00:25:20.705 --> 00:25:22.505
Then have this.

00:25:24.385 --> 00:25:25.265
Liver.

00:25:25.865 --> 00:25:27.705
If you weren’t my friend,
you wouldn’t get this either.

00:25:31.265 --> 00:25:32.425
Like it?

00:25:32.505 --> 00:25:34.505
Love it. How did you know I like liver?

00:25:34.585 --> 00:25:35.425
You like it, huh?

00:25:35.505 --> 00:25:36.625
And it’s sweet.

00:25:38.985 --> 00:25:42.505
And Nava,
let's go on the bike trip this Saturday.

00:25:43.745 --> 00:25:45.185
Sure, I'm in.

00:25:45.705 --> 00:25:48.105
It'll be much more fun if you're there.

00:25:48.185 --> 00:25:49.425
Sweet talker!

00:26:36.985 --> 00:26:38.305
What are you doing here?

00:26:39.305 --> 00:26:40.345
Why?

00:26:41.385 --> 00:26:43.625
Can't I come and watch you sing?

00:26:46.945 --> 00:26:48.065
You can.

00:26:58.305 --> 00:27:01.105
I'm heading back after this can.
Need to check on my grandma.

00:27:02.065 --> 00:27:03.385
She’s not well.

00:27:04.905 --> 00:27:06.065
Mm-hmm.

00:27:11.665 --> 00:27:13.265
If you love someone,

00:27:13.345 --> 00:27:16.385
you must let them know.

00:27:16.465 --> 00:27:18.345
Don't leave them guessing

00:27:18.425 --> 00:27:21.945
how they feel about you
or you feel about them.

00:27:22.025 --> 00:27:25.385
Otherwise, that love might turn into hate.

00:27:26.785 --> 00:27:27.945
DinDin,

00:27:30.665 --> 00:27:32.505
are you coming on the bike trip with me?

00:27:34.585 --> 00:27:35.785
I have to go anyway.

00:27:36.305 --> 00:27:37.665
I’m your employee.

00:27:38.865 --> 00:27:41.305
No… I mean, yeah, I know that.

00:27:42.105 --> 00:27:43.265
What I meant was…

00:27:45.465 --> 00:27:47.385
do you want to go biking with me?

00:27:48.945 --> 00:27:50.625
Like riding right by my side.

00:27:57.545 --> 00:27:59.585
If you want me by your side,

00:28:00.665 --> 00:28:02.025
then I’ll go.

00:29:15.625 --> 00:29:17.025
If this treatment

00:29:17.705 --> 00:29:20.065
is like riding a bike, as you just said.

00:29:21.185 --> 00:29:22.185
Now,

00:29:24.585 --> 00:29:26.985
you’ve cycled far away and left me behind.

00:29:57.905 --> 00:29:58.945
Sailom!

00:30:03.505 --> 00:30:04.505
Wait!

00:30:05.025 --> 00:30:06.545
I’m sorry!

00:30:38.225 --> 00:30:39.305
Sailom,

00:30:41.865 --> 00:30:43.945
I know I let you down.

00:30:45.585 --> 00:30:47.985
I failed you by not being your doctor.

00:30:48.585 --> 00:30:50.425
But know this…

00:30:51.865 --> 00:30:54.065
I never had any intention
of leaving you behind.

00:30:56.025 --> 00:30:58.505
The reason I’m here today is to apologize.

00:30:59.545 --> 00:31:01.705
Even if I can't be your doctor,

00:31:02.745 --> 00:31:04.225
I promise you.

00:31:05.505 --> 00:31:08.265
I will do everything in my power
to help you get better.

00:31:09.465 --> 00:31:10.825
Please, trust me.

00:31:20.745 --> 00:31:22.705
Yes, Pi Doc.

00:31:42.345 --> 00:31:44.985
If therapy is like riding a bike,

00:31:47.825 --> 00:31:50.345
are you ready to ride along with me?

00:31:59.945 --> 00:32:00.985
Yes.

00:33:16.105 --> 00:33:17.585
Let’s do this together.

00:33:24.825 --> 00:33:25.665
Yes.

00:34:29.385 --> 00:34:31.824
-Beautiful, isn't it?
-Yeah.

00:34:36.385 --> 00:34:37.505
The view or the person?

00:34:39.145 --> 00:34:39.985
The person.

00:34:42.145 --> 00:34:44.945
I brought you some water.

00:34:49.705 --> 00:34:51.105
Are you this kind to everyone?

00:34:52.185 --> 00:34:54.344
Nope. Just you.

00:34:58.585 --> 00:35:00.945
-What’s your name?
-I’m Soda.

00:35:01.025 --> 00:35:02.705
-And you?
-Lemon.

00:35:03.225 --> 00:35:05.505
We’re a good match. Lemon and Soda.

00:35:05.585 --> 00:35:07.985
-Are you imagining things?
-No.

00:35:08.065 --> 00:35:10.745
Haven't you ever had a "Lemon Soda" drink?

00:35:11.505 --> 00:35:12.745
And do you like it?

00:35:14.305 --> 00:35:15.425
I love it.

00:35:15.945 --> 00:35:17.265
Don’t you?

00:35:18.305 --> 00:35:19.545
I do.

00:35:21.625 --> 00:35:23.145
Aren't you going to have some water?

00:35:23.225 --> 00:35:24.545
I already did.

00:35:32.305 --> 00:35:33.145
Have some?

00:35:53.225 --> 00:35:54.505
Nava…

00:35:55.505 --> 00:35:57.065
-look at you.
-Dying.

00:35:57.145 --> 00:35:59.185
Can you get up? Come on.

00:36:03.505 --> 00:36:04.905
Oh, my.

00:36:04.985 --> 00:36:05.825
Argh!

00:36:05.905 --> 00:36:07.065
Look,

00:36:08.465 --> 00:36:09.505
you're covered in sand.

00:36:10.945 --> 00:36:12.345
Are you really okay?

00:36:12.425 --> 00:36:13.865
I'm fine. Gotta sit down.

00:36:19.505 --> 00:36:20.385
Here… water.

00:36:21.665 --> 00:36:22.625
Thanks.

00:36:29.985 --> 00:36:32.865
I didn't think… I'd make it this far.

00:36:34.225 --> 00:36:36.505
Why? Are you exhausted?

00:36:37.545 --> 00:36:39.065
Yes, I am.

00:36:39.825 --> 00:36:40.865
But…

00:36:42.425 --> 00:36:43.465
it feels good.

00:36:59.145 --> 00:37:00.265
First time seeing this side of you.

00:37:03.785 --> 00:37:04.865
Which side?

00:37:05.585 --> 00:37:07.825
You know… the side that isn't a host.

00:37:08.585 --> 00:37:10.745
The athlete side. The cyclist side.

00:37:14.625 --> 00:37:15.585
And…

00:37:16.185 --> 00:37:17.425
is it a good side?

00:37:19.785 --> 00:37:21.985
Yeah… it's good.

00:37:26.465 --> 00:37:27.465
Do you like it?

00:37:30.985 --> 00:37:32.265
I do.

00:37:36.945 --> 00:37:37.945
Like it how?

00:37:41.745 --> 00:37:43.145
As a friend.

00:37:45.545 --> 00:37:47.105
Then…

00:37:47.185 --> 00:37:49.385
let's keep riding together like this.

00:37:52.745 --> 00:37:53.585
Mm.

00:37:54.305 --> 00:37:55.785
For as long as I can handle it.

00:38:01.225 --> 00:38:02.465
Let's go.

00:38:06.545 --> 00:38:07.465
Careful there.

00:38:12.865 --> 00:38:15.065
Alright, everyone! It’s time!

00:38:15.145 --> 00:38:17.105
Now, it’s time to head back!

00:38:17.185 --> 00:38:18.745
And remember, this is very important!

00:38:18.825 --> 00:38:22.225
Check your safety gear
and make sure everything is ready!

00:38:22.745 --> 00:38:23.985
Alright! Let's go!

00:38:33.265 --> 00:38:34.505
Whoa! Hey!

00:38:35.785 --> 00:38:37.385
Are you okay?

00:38:39.865 --> 00:38:40.785
You alright?

00:38:42.425 --> 00:38:43.905
-Hey!
-Let me go!

00:38:43.985 --> 00:38:45.905
-Whoa, calm down!
-Go away!

00:38:47.025 --> 00:38:48.465
What's wrong? I'm just trying to help.

00:38:48.545 --> 00:38:52.425
-Don't touch me!
-Relax, I'm just helping.

00:38:52.505 --> 00:38:54.025
Get away from me!

00:38:54.105 --> 00:38:55.625
-Hey, take it--
-I said don't touch me!

00:38:55.705 --> 00:38:58.385
-Tawan, move back!
-Leave me!

00:39:05.225 --> 00:39:07.745
Sailom. Sailom.

00:39:12.625 --> 00:39:13.945
I'm right here.

00:39:16.585 --> 00:39:18.505
Can you hear me?

00:39:21.745 --> 00:39:23.545
I understand you, Sailom.

00:39:29.225 --> 00:39:31.505
Take a deep breath. Slowly…

00:39:38.585 --> 00:39:40.825
Look into my eyes, okay?

00:39:43.305 --> 00:39:45.025
Look at me.

00:39:59.745 --> 00:40:01.465
Breathe in…

00:40:04.425 --> 00:40:06.425
and breathe out slowly.

00:40:22.465 --> 00:40:23.625
I'm sorry.

00:40:24.905 --> 00:40:26.905
-I'm… so sorry, Pi Doc.
-Nong Sailom.

00:40:28.745 --> 00:40:31.345
You don't have to apologize.

00:40:31.425 --> 00:40:33.305
You did nothing wrong.

00:40:38.705 --> 00:40:40.625
I’m right here with you.

00:40:55.345 --> 00:40:56.945
Hey, Sailom.

00:40:57.025 --> 00:40:59.785
Are you still stressing about
what happened on the bike trip?

00:41:00.705 --> 00:41:01.665
Of course I am.

00:41:01.745 --> 00:41:03.825
I totally ruined his trip.

00:41:04.625 --> 00:41:06.985
Ruined it how? Everything went fine.

00:41:07.065 --> 00:41:08.705
Everyone made it back home safely.

00:41:08.785 --> 00:41:10.065
Nobody got hurt.

00:41:10.665 --> 00:41:12.785
But they were all shocked because of me.

00:41:13.385 --> 00:41:15.305
If it wasn't for my condition,

00:41:16.545 --> 00:41:18.825
Pi Doc's trip
wouldn't have been so disrupted.

00:41:20.145 --> 00:41:21.905
You're overthinking it.

00:41:21.985 --> 00:41:23.465
Pi Doc didn't even say a word about it.

00:41:24.465 --> 00:41:26.025
Or maybe he did, but we don't know?

00:41:26.625 --> 00:41:29.705
If your mouth is so free,
just stuff it with this!

00:41:30.505 --> 00:41:31.425
Damn you!

00:41:34.345 --> 00:41:36.985
Ugh! What am I going to do?!

00:41:39.745 --> 00:41:42.105
-Thank you for coming.
-Yes.

00:41:42.185 --> 00:41:43.345
Thank you.

00:41:44.145 --> 00:41:46.225
-Okay! Bye!
-Bye!

00:41:46.305 --> 00:41:47.825
What can I get for you?

00:41:47.905 --> 00:41:50.785
A cheesecake and a Thai tea, please.

00:41:50.865 --> 00:41:52.945
A cheesecake and a Thai tea… and?

00:41:53.025 --> 00:41:55.345
-A pink milk, please.
-Got it.

00:41:55.425 --> 00:41:56.865
Wow, we're really busy today.

00:41:57.945 --> 00:42:00.625
It's been non-stop
since the bike trip ended.

00:42:01.385 --> 00:42:03.545
Oh, please help make some more desserts.

00:42:03.625 --> 00:42:06.625
Sure thing. As soon as I
finish making this cup.

00:42:06.705 --> 00:42:08.105
-Thank you.
-Of course.

00:42:11.785 --> 00:42:15.105
Does the chain come off
when you're picking up speed?

00:42:15.185 --> 00:42:16.665
Please park over here.

00:42:16.745 --> 00:42:20.385
I think it's an issue with the gears.
Please have a seat and wait.

00:42:20.465 --> 00:42:21.625
Thank you.

00:42:25.705 --> 00:42:27.465
You can wait over here.

00:42:27.545 --> 00:42:29.465
-OK.
-Or if you'd like some coffee,

00:42:29.545 --> 00:42:30.905
we have a café over there.

00:42:30.985 --> 00:42:33.105
I think I'll wait at the café.

00:42:33.185 --> 00:42:34.265
Certainly. Right this way.

00:42:46.065 --> 00:42:47.545
How long will you stand there?

00:42:48.585 --> 00:42:49.905
Help me fix these.

00:42:53.225 --> 00:42:55.345
Stop posing already. Hurry up.

00:42:55.425 --> 00:42:56.545
Fine.

00:42:57.185 --> 00:42:58.385
Help me take this wheel off.

00:43:00.185 --> 00:43:01.345
Hey, Tawan!

00:43:02.505 --> 00:43:04.425
Can you edit a clip for our page?

00:43:05.065 --> 00:43:06.985
Look at all these bikes around you.

00:43:12.105 --> 00:43:13.985
Ever since your bike trip ended,

00:43:14.745 --> 00:43:16.985
the shop's been flooded!

00:43:19.585 --> 00:43:21.505
Forget about editing clips.

00:43:21.585 --> 00:43:23.145
I don't even have time to breathe.

00:43:26.265 --> 00:43:28.305
By the way, how’s that kid doing?

00:43:29.145 --> 00:43:29.985
Which kid?

00:43:30.865 --> 00:43:32.665
The kid who freaked out.

00:43:34.585 --> 00:43:36.345
Oh, you mean Sailom?

00:43:37.945 --> 00:43:39.785
You saw it yourself.

00:43:39.865 --> 00:43:41.465
He can’t be touched.

00:43:41.545 --> 00:43:45.425
Is this the patient
you told Sky and me about that time?

00:43:46.465 --> 00:43:47.305
Yep.

00:43:48.905 --> 00:43:50.025
That's a tough one.

00:43:50.625 --> 00:43:51.825
Good luck with that.

00:44:03.905 --> 00:44:05.305
How many more bikes are left?

00:44:07.785 --> 00:44:13.505
Give it a try for a couple of days.
It should be working fine now.

00:44:13.585 --> 00:44:16.345
I just had my mechanic
double-check and test everything.

00:44:16.865 --> 00:44:18.945
Alright! Okay! Thank you so much.

00:44:19.025 --> 00:44:23.505
If you run into any more issues,
just let us know. We're happy to help.

00:44:23.585 --> 00:44:25.585
-Yes, thank you.
-You’re welcome.

00:44:30.385 --> 00:44:31.345
Sailom?

00:44:44.185 --> 00:44:45.985
You’re here to see me, right?

00:44:52.065 --> 00:44:54.585
If there’s anything you want to say,

00:44:54.665 --> 00:44:55.705
I’m listening.

00:44:59.425 --> 00:45:02.585
I’m so sorry for ruining your trip.

00:45:04.345 --> 00:45:06.305
I really didn't mean it.

00:45:06.385 --> 00:45:07.945
Please don't be mad at me.

00:45:09.585 --> 00:45:12.625
If there's anything I can do to help,

00:45:12.705 --> 00:45:14.025
please tell me.

00:45:14.825 --> 00:45:17.145
I don't want to feel guilty anymore.

00:45:19.305 --> 00:45:21.425
You didn't do anything wrong.

00:45:24.025 --> 00:45:28.225
If you’re worried that I'm angry,
don't be.

00:45:28.305 --> 00:45:29.665
I'm not mad at all.

00:45:30.665 --> 00:45:31.985
I actually understand.

00:45:34.825 --> 00:45:35.945
Really?

00:45:37.345 --> 00:45:38.425
Really.

00:45:43.505 --> 00:45:46.545
I actually am looking for some help.

00:45:47.865 --> 00:45:49.225
Know how to edit videos?

00:45:50.145 --> 00:45:52.425
-Edit videos?
-Yes.

00:45:53.145 --> 00:45:56.305
I need someone to edit
the bike trip clips for our page.

00:45:57.025 --> 00:45:57.945
Can you do that?

00:45:59.985 --> 00:46:02.065
Yes! I can do that!

00:46:08.025 --> 00:46:09.505
Hurry up!

00:46:09.585 --> 00:46:11.065
Yeah, I'm on it.

00:46:11.945 --> 00:46:14.105
Wait! Keep this part.

00:46:14.185 --> 00:46:15.665
This shot is beautiful.

00:46:15.745 --> 00:46:17.785
-Put this clip right here!
-Geez.

00:46:18.545 --> 00:46:20.265
Why don't you do it yourself?

00:46:22.225 --> 00:46:23.865
Here’s the mouse.

00:46:28.185 --> 00:46:29.385
Please, continue.

00:46:30.505 --> 00:46:33.425
I promise I’ll be quiet.

00:46:33.505 --> 00:46:35.265
Not a peep from me.

00:46:35.345 --> 00:46:37.665
If you can't even edit,
why did you volunteer?

00:46:39.425 --> 00:46:41.945
Pi Doc couldn't find anyone to help.

00:46:42.785 --> 00:46:46.025
I must do anything
I can do to help him. Right?

00:46:46.105 --> 00:46:47.505
Want to help your boyfriend, huh?

00:46:48.105 --> 00:46:49.465
Come on!

00:46:49.545 --> 00:46:51.425
We’re just doctor and patient!

00:46:52.265 --> 00:46:53.945
We’re not dating.

00:46:54.625 --> 00:46:55.865
Really?

00:46:57.185 --> 00:47:00.185
But the doctor’s necklace
is around the patient’s neck.

00:47:09.385 --> 00:47:11.425
You better buy me beers after this.

00:47:12.345 --> 00:47:14.945
Fine. I'll buy you a whole factory.

00:47:15.025 --> 00:47:17.265
Perfect. Now, I'm motivated.

00:47:18.345 --> 00:47:19.945
Keep the orders coming.

00:47:22.305 --> 00:47:24.945
Oh, this music isn't quite right.

00:47:25.025 --> 00:47:26.745
-This one is better.
-Copy that.

00:47:26.825 --> 00:47:27.745
Go ahead.

00:47:41.745 --> 00:47:43.105
Time really flies, doesn't it?

00:47:44.025 --> 00:47:48.225
It feels like just yesterday
we were all having dinner together.

00:47:48.305 --> 00:47:50.025
It really does, Mom.

00:47:50.785 --> 00:47:54.185
Remember what your dad told you?

00:47:54.865 --> 00:47:56.465
No matter what happens,

00:47:56.985 --> 00:47:58.745
love one another.

00:47:59.265 --> 00:48:02.025
Because family
is the most important thing.

00:48:03.665 --> 00:48:04.745
We remember, Mom.

00:48:05.425 --> 00:48:07.065
But we still fight all the time.

00:48:08.625 --> 00:48:11.545
-It happens.
-I know.

00:48:11.625 --> 00:48:14.505
You can fight, but once it’s over,

00:48:14.585 --> 00:48:16.425
always forgive each other.

00:48:17.345 --> 00:48:19.185
I miss Dad.

00:48:20.585 --> 00:48:22.745
I miss him too.

00:48:26.345 --> 00:48:28.185
So, what's for dinner tonight?

00:48:29.785 --> 00:48:31.745
A seafood BBQ by the beach?

00:48:32.745 --> 00:48:35.505
Can… I invite my friends over?

00:48:37.505 --> 00:48:38.905
If you do, I’m inviting mine too.

00:48:39.465 --> 00:48:42.345
Good. I’ll invite the kids
from the shop to join us.

00:48:42.865 --> 00:48:43.825
‎Right?

00:49:19.625 --> 00:49:21.025
Who do you live here with?

00:49:28.665 --> 00:49:29.625
Well…

00:49:31.385 --> 00:49:34.505
my parents split up when I was a kid.

00:49:36.625 --> 00:49:38.705
And back then,
I chose to stay with my mom.

00:49:39.905 --> 00:49:42.105
Maybe my dad is still mad at me

00:49:42.625 --> 00:49:43.945
because I didn't choose him.

00:49:46.265 --> 00:49:47.465
The truth is…

00:49:47.545 --> 00:49:49.625
I never wanted to choose at all.

00:49:52.505 --> 00:49:54.465
Because no matter who I chose…

00:49:55.785 --> 00:49:57.705
I would still be the one at fault.

00:50:12.225 --> 00:50:13.785
Never had a boyfriend.

00:50:13.865 --> 00:50:15.585
Then… give me a kiss.

00:50:16.425 --> 00:50:20.065
A host and a customer.
Is it really possible?

00:50:20.865 --> 00:50:23.425
Take this home, so your
grandma can have a warm meal.

00:50:24.945 --> 00:50:27.105
Grandma?! Grandma!

00:50:27.185 --> 00:50:29.665
Your grandma is going to be okay.

00:50:31.185 --> 00:50:32.545
I want to see Nabnueng.

00:50:34.425 --> 00:50:36.105
It's been a long time, Son.

00:50:39.665 --> 00:50:41.545
-No!
-Sailom!